---
import MainLayout from "../../layouts/MainLayout.astro";

const title = "Real Estate Listing Description Prompts | Realty Efficiency Hub";
const description =
  "Practical AI prompts for writing better real estate listing descriptions with ChatGPT and other AI tools.";
---

<MainLayout title={title} description={description}>
  <article style="max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;">
    <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #64748b; margin-bottom: 10px;">
      Blog
    </p>

    <h1 style="font-size: 42px; margin-bottom: 18px;">
      Real Estate Listing Description Prompts
    </h1>

    <p style="font-size: 19px; color: #475569; line-height: 1.7;">
      Writing property descriptions can be repetitive and time-consuming.
      AI tools can help real estate professionals draft faster, improve tone,
      and tailor listings to different buyer profiles. The key is using better prompts.
    </p>

    <p style="font-size: 19px; color: #475569; line-height: 1.7;">
      Below are practical prompt examples you can adapt for homes, apartments,
      luxury properties, investment listings, and more.
    </p>

    <h2 style="margin-top: 40px; font-size: 30px;">Prompt 1 — General Listing Description</h2>

    <div style="background: white; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius: 12px; padding: 20px; margin-top: 16px;">
      <p style="margin: 0; white-space: pre-line; line-height: 1.7;">
Write a compelling real estate listing description for a [property type] in [location].
Highlight the following features: [features].
Target audience: [first-time buyers / families / investors / luxury buyers].
Tone: professional, warm, and persuasive.
Keep it under 180 words.
      </p>
    </div>

    <h2 style="margin-top: 40px; font-size: 30px;">Prompt 2 — Luxury Property Version</h2>

    <div style="background: white; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius: 12px; padding: 20px; margin-top: 16px;">
      <p style="margin: 0; white-space: pre-line; line-height: 1.7;">
Create a luxury real estate listing description for a [property type] in [location].
Emphasize exclusivity, design, finishes, and lifestyle appeal.
Include these features: [features].
Use an elegant and refined tone.
Keep it concise and high-end.
      </p>
    </div>

    <h2 style="margin-top: 40px; font-size: 30px;">Prompt 3 — Investor-Focused Version</h2>

    <div style="background: white; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius: 12px; padding: 20px; margin-top: 16px;">
      <p style="margin: 0; white-space: pre-line; line-height: 1.7;">
Write a listing description for an investment property in [location].
Focus on rental potential, yield drivers, location benefits, and renovation upside.
Property details: [details].
Tone: professional and data-aware.
Keep it under 160 words.
      </p>
    </div>

    <h2 style="margin-top: 40px; font-size: 30px;">How to use these prompts well</h2>

    <ul style="line-height: 1.9; color: #475569; font-size: 18px;">
      <li>Add precise property facts instead of generic adjectives.</li>
      <li>Specify the buyer type to improve relevance.</li>
      <li>Ask the AI to rewrite for different tones and channels.</li>
      <li>Edit the final draft to reflect the real property accurately.</li>
    </ul>

    <p style="margin-top: 40px; font-size: 18px; color: #475569; line-height: 1.7;">
      Related hub:
      <a href="/ai-prompts" style="color: #2563eb; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600;">
        AI Prompts for Real Estate Professionals
      </a>
    </p>
  </article>
</MainLayout>